{
  "doc_id": "35748",
  "text": "The HOS-Brazil exhibited excellent intra-rater testretest reliability, with an ICC of 0.992 for the ADL subscale and 0.994 for the Sports subscale. An ICC ranging from 0.4 to 0.75 is considered satisfactory, whereas values ≥0.75 are considered excellent [CITATION_1] . The analysis showed that all of the ICC values resulting from the comparison of the first and second application were over 0.9 for both subscales. This finding indicates high intrarater test-retest reliability and shows that the HOS-Brazil is reliable. The time interval between the test and retest was 48 h.",
